Class Flak

  • java.lang.Object
    • Flak
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IsAttachableToTruck
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CarTransportFlak
    public class Flak
extends java.lang.Object
implements IsAttachableToTruck
    Flak is a Class that implements IsAttachableToTruck. Is made to allow trucks to have additioinal functions and is also a standard for future flak-designs Contains coordinates and a variable for the truck it is currently attached to Also contains a value for the angle of the flak. What this represents is up to the creator of the flak to decide
    Author:
    pepegas
